[[波蘭|波蘭]]是歐洲信仰虔誠的國家之一<ref name="cbos">{{cite web |language=pl |publisher=<!--Centrum Badania Opinii Społecznej-->[[Centre_for_Public_Opinion_Research|Centre for Public Opinion Research]] CBOS |location=Warsaw |date=March 2005 |url=http://www.cbos.pl/SPISKOM.POL/2005/K_049_05.PDF |title=Co łączy Polaków z parafią? Komunikat z badań |trans-title=What Connects Poles with Parish? Training Message |at=Preface |access-date=14 December 2007}}</ref> ，儘管波蘭有著不同的宗教社群，但大多數波蘭人大都信奉[[基督宗教|基督宗教]]。在基督信仰中最大的群體是[[羅馬天主教會|羅馬天主教會]]：在2015 年有92.9% 的人口波蘭人表示自己屬於該教派（由中央統計局 (GUS) 進行的人口普查）<ref name="GUS2016">{{Cite web|url=https://stat.gov.pl/en/infographics-and-widgets/infographics/infographic-religiousness-of-polish-inhabitiants,4,1.html|title=Infographic - Religiousness of Polish inhabitiants|last=GUS|website=stat.gov.pl|language=en|access-date=2019-06-17}}</ref><ref name="GUS99">GUS, ''[http://stat.gov.pl/download/cps/rde/xbcr/gus/LUD_ludnosc_stan_str_dem_spo_NSP2011.pdf Narodowy Spis Powszechny Ludnosci 2011: 4.4. Przynależność wyznaniowa (National Survey 2011: 4.4 Membership in faith communities)]'' p. 99/337 (PDF file, direct download 3.3 MB). {{ISBN|978-83-7027-521-1}} {{nobreak| Retrieved 27 December 2014.}}</ref>，根據天主教會統計研究所的數據，2015 年有 36.7% 的波蘭天主教信徒會參加主日[[彌撒|彌撒]]。<ref>{{cite book |url= http://iskk.pl/images/stories/Instytut/dokumenty/Annuarium_Statisticum_2018.pdf |title= Annuarium Statisticum Ecclesiae in Polonia AD 2018 |year= 2018 |editor1-last= Sadłoń |editor1-first= Wojciech |publisher= Instytut Statystyki Kościoła Katolickiego SAC |location= Warszawa |language= pl |page= 4 |doi= 10.13140/RG.2.2.23260.90248|last1= Sadlon |first1= Wojciech }}</ref>史學家 Neal Pease 將波蘭描述為「[[聖座|聖座]]最忠實的女兒」。<ref>{{cite book|title=Rome's Most Faithful Daughter: The Catholic Church and Independent Poland, 1914–1939|last=Pease|first=Neal|publisher=Ohio University Press|year=2009|isbn=9780821443620}}</ref>

[[天主教會|天主教會]]在許多波蘭人的生活中仍然很重要，天主教會在波蘭享有社會聲望和政治影響<ref>{{cite web|url= http://www.britannica.com/EBchecked/topic/466681/Poland#tab=active~checked%2Citems~checked&title=Poland%20--%20Britannica%20Online%20Encyclopedia|publisher= [[Encyclopædia_Britannica|Encyclopædia Britannica]] |title= Religion in Poland|access-date= 9 January 2018}}</ref> ，被視為波蘭文化遺產的寶庫<ref>[http://encarta.msn.com/encyclopedia_761559758_4/Poland.html#s13]  {{webarchive|url= https://web.archive.org/web/20090401142722/http://encarta.msn.com/encyclopedia_761559758_4/Poland.html |date= 1 April 2009 }}</ref>。波蘭聲稱天主教教友的人數在歐洲第三多，僅次於[[馬爾他|馬爾他]]和[[聖馬利諾|聖馬利諾]]（人數多於[[義大利|義大利]]、[[西班牙|西班牙]]和[[愛爾蘭|愛爾蘭]]，這些國家都以天主教為主要信仰宗派）。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.theguardian.com/world/2018/mar/21/christianity-non-christian-europe-young-people-survey-religion|title='Christianity as default is gone': the rise of a non-Christian Europe|date=21 March 2018|website=the Guardian}}</ref>

天主教教友在波蘭有如此高的比例主要是由於[[納粹德國|納粹德國]]對在侵略波蘭時[[納粹大屠殺|對猶太人進行屠殺]]和二戰期間波蘭少數宗教群體的傷亡，<ref name="posterum0">Project in Posterum, [http://www.projectinposterum.org/docs/poland_WWII_casualties.htm Poland World War II casualties.] Retrieved 20 September 2013.</ref><ref name="5MillionForgotten0">[http://www.remember.org/forgotten/ Holocaust: Five Million Forgotten: Non-Jewish Victims of the Shoah.] Remember.org.</ref><ref name=expatica>AFP/Expatica, ''[http://www.expatica.com/de/news/german-news/Polish-experts-lower-nation_s-WWII-death-toll--_55843.html Polish experts lower nation's WWII death toll]'', Expatica.com, 30 August 2009</ref><ref name=szma>[[Tomasz_Szarota|Tomasz Szarota]] & Wojciech Materski, ''Polska 1939–1945. Straty osobowe i ofiary represji pod dwiema okupacjami'', Warsaw, IPN 2009, {{ISBN| 978-83-7629-067-6}} ([http://niniwa2.cba.pl/polska_1939_1945.htm Introduction online.] {{webarchive|url= https://web.archive.org/web/20130201065133/http://niniwa2.cba.pl/polska_1939_1945.htm |date= 1 February 2013 }})</ref> 以及在二戰結束後[[第二次世界大戰戰後對德意志人的驅逐|波蘭對德意志裔的驅逐]]，這些被驅逐者大都不是天主教教友。

除了天主教外，波蘭的其他基督信仰還包括[[東儀天主教會|東儀天主教會]]<ref name="MRS" /> 、[[東正教|東正教]]（[[波蘭正教會|正教會]]）<ref name="MRS" /> 、[[新教|新教]]（其中最大教派為{{link-en|波蘭奧格斯堡福音派教會|Evangelical Church of the Augsburg Confession in Poland}}）<ref name="MRS" /> 和[[耶和華見證人|耶和華見證人]]<ref name="MRS" /> 。

不到 0.1% 的波蘭人口信奉的其他宗教，包括[[伊斯蘭教|伊斯蘭教]]、[[猶太教|猶太教]]、[[印度教|印度教]]和[[佛教|佛教]]。<ref>
